project_descr: The overall objective of the programme is: “To ensure that the people, economy and environment of Seychelles are able to adapt to and develop resilience to climate change and its effects, thereby safeguarding the sustainable development of Seychelles”.

outputs.output_descr: Supporting adaptation to climate change to increase coastal and flood protection in the vulnerable areas of La Digue Island

project_title: global climate change alliance seychelles programme
